name: MLMultiArrayDataType
desc: Constants that define the underlying element types a multiarray can store.

items.name: case int32
items.desc: Designates the multiarray’s elements as 32-bit integers.

items.name: case float32
items.desc: Designates the multiarray’s elements as 32-bit floats.

items.name: case double
items.desc: Designates the multiarray’s elements as doubles.

items.name: static var float: MLMultiArrayDataType
items.desc: Designates the multiarray’s elements as floats.

items.name: static var float64: MLMultiArrayDataType
items.desc: Designates the multiarray’s elements as 64-bit floats.
